  <div class="intro">
    <div id="nomadPicture"><img class="nomad" src="images/greenNomad.png"></div>

    <div id="jimmynomad">
      <h2>Hey! I'm Jimmy Nomad.</h2>
      <span class="founder"><h3>The founder of Nomadsland.</h3></span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="loveithere">
    <div class="loveItHereText">
    <h3>You are going to love it here!</h3>
    <span id="showYouAround">
      <h3>I can't wait to show you around...</h3>
    </span></div>
  </div>

  <div class="elevate">
    <h3>First we gotta elevate.<br>
      Elevation <span class="power">powers</span> this place!</h3>
    <p>
      <span class="itseasy">It's really easy! Scroll & I'll explain</span>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="worldKnowledge">
    <h3><span class="elevAndWorld">Elevation</span> = <span class="elevAndWorld">Travel Knowledge</span></h3>
    <p>You elevate by answering basic questions about places you have traveled to:</p>
  </div>
  <div class="questions">
    <h3>When were you there?<br>
      Was it fun?<br>
      How was the food?<br>
      How was the sightseeing?<br>
      How did the locals treat you?<br>
      How affordable was it?<br>
    </h3>
  </div>
  <div class="itsSimple">
    <img id="cookingPicture" src="/images/cooking.jpg">
    <img id="barPicture" src="/images/bar.jpg">
    <div class="andIfYouSaw">
      <h3>& if you did, ate, or saw anything awesome, tell me about it to boost your elevation even more!</h3>
      <span class="itsThatSimple">
        <p>it's that simple</p>
      </span>
    </div>
    <img id="trailerPicture" src="/images/trailer.jpg">

  </div>
  <div class="usesElevation">
    <div class="usesElevationText">
    <h3>Nomadsland uses elevation to inform + inspire modern explorers everywhere</h3>
    <span class="needYourHelp"><p>And this is where I need you...</p></span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="elevateNow">
    <h3>...because I need <span class="your">YOUR</span> elevation!</h3>
    <span class="sendUs"><p>Click the Nomadicon to elevate now</p>
      <p>+<br><span class="pursue">#pursuetheplanet</span> in your Nomadicon tee and send me pics on IG!
      </p>
      <a href="/login"><img src="/images/nomad.png" width="35" height="35"></a>
  </div>
  </div>
